short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Change the default omnibox (address bar) search to Predator Search.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Change default search engine to make Predator Search your default search in Chrome omnibox (address bar).
Predator Search is a useful Google Chrome extension that helps you change your default search engine in address bar of the browser to Predator Search very easily.
Click on «Keep it» button to leave the default search Predator Search and make sure of the best search experience.

Terms of Use: https://predatorwallpaper.com/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://predatorwallpaper.com/privacy.html

By click on «Add to Chrome» button in the top right hand corner and installing the Predator Search extension, you are agreeing to install this extension, you are agreeing to our Privacy Policy, and you are agreeing to our Terms of Use.
